```mermaid
graph TD
    A[User Interface (CLI)] --> B[Command Modules]
    B --> C[Reporting Engine]
    B --> D[Vulnerability Scan Engine]
    C --> E[Platform APIs]
    D --> F[Local Logs]
    F --> G[JSON DB]
